short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Adds a keyboard shortcut to select the previously viewed tab.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Select previously viewed tab by pressing Alt-Q (Ctrl-Q on Mac). The shortcut can be configured.

This extension:
— Has no tracking
— Can't read your tabs
— Doesn't consume any memory or CPU when not used

Source code: github.com/NV/select-previous-tab
